            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Bono Deo <lb n="2"/>Puero P<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>os</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="3"/>phoro <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Italicus <lb n="5"/>primus IIII<lb break="no" n="6"/>vir <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ureli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>pulensis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>cum Stati<lb break="no" n="8"/>lia Lucia <lb n="9"/>coniuge et <lb n="10"/>suis ex voto
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Statuenbasis. Datierung: Apulum wurde unter Mark Aurel municipium, unter Commodus colonia.</p>
            </div>
